00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:50,400
But

639
00:32:50,650 --> 00:32:52,800
from the moment you put on your uniform,

640
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:53,590
I hope

641
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:54,430
you can hold yourself

642
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:56,320
to the standard of firefighters.

643
00:32:56,370 --> 00:32:56,870
Understand?

644
00:32:56,910 --> 00:32:57,630
Yes.

645
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,940
Okay. Next, I will explain to everyone

646
00:33:00,150 --> 00:33:02,290
