647
00:33:02,670 --> 00:33:03,630
Take off your sneakers.

648
00:33:04,050 --> 00:33:06,910
Put your feet directly into the protective boots.

649
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:08,800
Pull up the belt.

650
00:33:42,060 --> 00:33:43,320
There will be a lot of smoke

651
