653
00:33:47,270 --> 00:33:48,400
In order to prevent

654
00:33:48,450 --> 00:33:49,660
anyone from getting lost,

655
00:33:49,890 --> 00:33:52,330
we choose to tie a rope around our waist

656
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:53,780
