00:34:03,860 --> 00:34:06,800
[Nanbin Special Division]

663
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:13,980
Nan Chu, hold my shoulder strap.

664
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:15,830
Nan Chu.

665
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:18,310
Pay attention. This is important.

666
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:19,570
Director Lin,

667
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,000
as a frontline firefighter,

668
00:34:22,050 --> 00:34:23,470
if I grab your shoulder strap

669
