00:34:26,790 --> 00:34:28,050
When we're at the scene

672
00:34:28,680 --> 00:34:30,450
and rescuing those who are conscious,

673
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:32,420
we'll choose to tie everyone together

674
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,740
and walk forward like this

675
00:34:35,990 --> 00:34:36,910
to avoid being separated.

676
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,670
Understand?

677
00:34:39,810 --> 00:34:41,830
Try with each other.

678
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:53,380
Did you want to form a ship with Director Lin?

