681
00:35:00,730 --> 00:35:02,870
I didn't.

682
00:35:08,920 --> 00:35:12,400
[Practice]

683
00:35:15,090 --> 00:35:15,680
Not bad.

684
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:19,290
As you can see,

685
00:35:19,750 --> 00:35:20,680
rope climbing

686
00:35:20,930 --> 00:35:23,660
is one of the necessary skills for firefighters.

687
00:35:24,040 --> 00:35:26,720
This skill is important

688
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:28,400
in many rescues and self-rescues.

689
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:30,210
Did you see

690
00:35:30,250 --> 00:35:31,300
Assistant Liu's demonstration clearly?

691
00:35:31,680 --> 00:35:32,690
Yes.

