00:35:32,690 --> 00:35:33,280
Okay.

693
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:37,010
Today, I'll teach you how to tie the knot.

694
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,060
Assistant Liu.

695
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:38,780
Yes.

696
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:40,210
Go down and guide them.

697
00:35:40,210 --> 00:35:40,670
Yes.

698
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:56,590
Everyone must remember the steps.

699
00:35:57,300 --> 00:35:59,060
Don't underestimate the basic training.

700
00:35:59,530 --> 00:36:01,080
This knot looks simple,

701
00:36:01,370 --> 00:36:03,010
but this is the most important part

702
00:36:03,010 --> 00:36:04,520
in high altitude rescues.

703
00:36:04,900 --> 00:36:06,080
It's known as the knot of life.

704
00:36:10,240 --> 00:36:10,910
Report!

705
00:36:15,490 --> 00:36:16,330
Tall guy,

706
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:17,710
you made the wrong knot.

707
00:36:18,050 --> 00:36:19,520
I know the kind that you taught,

708
00:36:19,770 --> 00:36:21,870
but mine is what veterans use overseas.

709
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:23,170
It's more convenient

710
00:36:23,170 --> 00:36:23,970
and saves more time than yours.

711
00:36:25,060 --> 00:36:25,900
Lin,

712
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:26,950
is it like this?

713
00:36:27,410 --> 00:36:29,470
His knot is fine,

714
00:36:29,470 --> 00:36:31,320
but it's not what we taught.

715
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:32,870
I guess you know a lot.

716
00:36:33,250 --> 00:36:33,920
It's fine.

717
00:36:34,470 --> 00:36:35,270
See?

718
00:36:35,310 --> 00:36:36,850
Director Lin said it's good.

719
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:38,040
By the way,

