00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:39,510
I heard you have

721
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:40,640
an unwritten rule here

722
00:36:41,320 --> 00:36:43,250
that if a new team member successfully challenges an old team member,

723
00:36:43,290 --> 00:36:44,930
you can add your own rule

724
00:36:44,930 --> 00:36:45,850
to the Special Division's Nine Rules.

725
00:36:46,270 --> 00:36:47,070
Is that true?

726
00:36:48,540 --> 00:36:50,220
Judging from your tone,

727
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:52,110
