00:37:43,890 --> 00:37:45,530
Mr. Jiang, you're amazing.

741
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:47,930
Not bad, I didn't forget everything.

742
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:49,900
You're not bad.

743
00:37:50,740 --> 00:37:51,830
During the training this afternoon,

744
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:53,890
you can help check

