746
00:37:56,080 --> 00:37:56,540
Sure.

747
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:00,220
Not bad.

748
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:02,670
It's a pity that you're not a firefighter.

749
00:38:03,720 --> 00:38:04,680
If I win you all,

