815
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:10,350
Alright, go ahead.

816
00:40:10,350 --> 00:40:11,310
-Yes.
-Thank you, Deputy Yu.

817
00:40:11,690 --> 00:40:12,070
Wait for me.

818
00:40:12,070 --> 00:40:12,360
Don't worry.

819
00:40:12,660 --> 00:40:12,910
Okay.

820
00:40:26,100 --> 00:40:27,020
Over there.

821
00:40:27,990 --> 00:40:28,530
Hello.

