824
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:33,870
Are you the homeowner here?

825
00:40:34,370 --> 00:40:35,920
Why else would I call you here?

826
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:37,350
Open the door!

827
00:40:37,730 --> 00:40:38,280
Sir.

828
00:40:38,700 --> 00:40:40,750
