00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:44,910
Shut up and open the door.

832
00:40:45,790 --> 00:40:46,800
Don't break in yet.

833
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:48,360
Deputy Director Yu is waiting for us downstairs.

834
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,320
According to the rules,

835
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,410
we can only break in

836
00:40:50,460 --> 00:40:51,380
if the leader is here.

837
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:52,300
We didn't bring a recorder.

838
00:40:52,300 --> 00:40:53,650
Who will take responsibility since he's drunk?

839
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:56,420
Shut up and open the door.

840
00:40:56,460 --> 00:40:58,350
