852
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:29,680
I sincerely apologize to you.

853
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:30,520
I'm sorry.

854
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:33,590
You think that saying they're inexperienced will resolve this?

855
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:36,230
I was almost scared to death.

856
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,070
If someone broke through your door

857
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:38,670
