858
00:41:38,670 --> 00:41:39,340
anyone would be scared.

859
00:41:39,930 --> 00:41:41,690
I don't care about your excuses.

860
00:41:41,690 --> 00:41:42,870
You must give me

861
00:41:42,870 --> 00:41:43,840
a reasonable explanation today.

862
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,010
Yes.

863
00:41:45,350 --> 00:41:47,570
We came after receiving a report.

864
00:41:47,910 --> 00:41:49,120
He gave the wrong info.

865
